'''拉克夫由'''（{{lang en|'''Lakeview'''}}）是[[美國|美國]][[俄勒岡州|俄勒岡州]][[萊克縣_(俄勒岡州)|萊克縣 (俄勒岡州)]]的縣治。{{GR|6}}根據[[美國2010年人口普查|2010年人口普查]]，本城共有人口2,294人。<ref name="2010 census">{{cite web|title=2010 Census profiles: Oregon cities alphabetically H-L|url=http://www.pdx.edu/sites/www.pdx.edu.prc/files/2010_PL94_cities_H-L_updated.pdf|publisher=Portland State University Population Research Center|accessdate=November 21, 2011|format=PDF|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20181107074041/https://www.pdx.edu/sites/www.pdx.edu.prc/files/2010_PL94_cities_H-L_updated.pdf|archive-date=2018-11-07|dead-url=yes}}</ref>本城的綽號為「俄勒岡州最高的城鎮」（The Tallest Town in Oregon），因為它是俄勒岡州海拔最高的城鎮。<ref name="tallest town">{{Cite web |url=http://www.lakevieworegon.org/home.html |title=Lakeview Oregon<!-- Bot generated title --> |access-date=2013-07-06 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20130408024358/http://www.lakevieworegon.org/home.html |archive-date=2013-04-08 |dead-url=yes }}</ref>

==歷史==
[[北美原住民|美國原住民]]在本城的足跡能追溯至9,000年前。<ref>{{cite web|title=Oregon Historical County Records Guide: Lake County History|url=http://arcweb.sos.state.or.us/pages/records/local/county/lake/hist.html|publisher=Oregon Secretary of State|year=2012|accessdate=July 6, 2013|archive-date=2011-11-03|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20111103185244/http://arcweb.sos.state.or.us/pages/records/local/county/lake/hist.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>白人探險家、商人和入侵者則於1800年代先後到達這裡。<ref name="lakecountymuseum.com">{{cite web|title=Local History Time Line |first=Norma |last=Lund |publisher=Lake County Museum |url=http://www.lakecountymuseum.com/Local%20History/timeline.html |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20070818000711/http://www.lakecountymuseum.com/Local%20History/timeline.html |archivedate=2007-08-18|date=January 30, 2007 |deadurl=yes }}</ref>這一帶的首個白人前哨為建於1866年的[[華納堡|華納堡]]。白人興建此前哨是為了保護白人免受土著襲擊。<ref name="County history">{{cite web| title = History of Lake County| publisher = Lake County Chamber of Commerce| url = http://www.lakecountychamber.org/history.html| accessdate = July 6, 2013| archive-date = 2017-03-24| archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20170324071336/http://www.lakecountychamber.org/history.html| dead-url = yes}}</ref>

[[喬治·克魯克|喬治·克魯克]]將軍於1870及1880年代活躍於這一帶，大量興建白人營地，佔領土著領土並殺戮土著。<ref name="lakecountymuseum.com"/>而當時的拉克夫由則成為了[[愛爾蘭人|愛爾蘭]]和[[巴斯克人|巴斯克]]牧羊人的聚居地。<ref>{{cite book|title=Speaking Through the Aspens: Basque Tree Carvings in Nevada and California|first=J.|last=Mallea-Olaetxe|pages=8, 36–37, 40, 104–105, 157, 190|series=The Basque Series|year=2000|publisher=University of Nevada Press|location=Reno, Nevada|edition=2008|isbn=978-0-87417-762-6|oclc=233936651}}</ref>

這一帶首個建立的鄉村為建於1869年的[[新松河_(俄勒岡州)|新松河]]。<ref name="lakecountymuseum.com"/>而郵局則於10年後的12月8日才建立。<ref name="OGN">{{cite book | last = McArthur | first = Lewis A. | authorlink = Lewis A. McArthur | coauthors = Lewis L. McArthur | title = Oregon Geographic Names | origyear = 1928 | edition = 7th | year = 2003 | publisher = [[Oregon_Historical_Society|Oregon Historical Society]] Press | location = Portland, Oregon| isbn = 0-87595-277-1 | page = 701 }}</ref>於1875年，拉克夫由現今所在的[[萊克縣_(俄勒岡州)|萊克縣]]自[[傑克遜縣_(俄勒岡州)|傑克遜縣]]和[[沃斯科縣|沃斯科縣]]成立。起初，萊克縣的縣治為領匯威樂（今[[克拉馬斯福爾斯_(俄勒岡州)|克拉馬斯福爾斯]]），但後來改為拉克夫充由當縣治。<ref name="County history"/>

於1890年，一場大火燒毀了本城75座建築物。本城於1901年完成重建，並以磚和鐵建造房屋。因此，儘管另一場大火於1906年侵襲本城，但僅僅數間房屋遭燒毀。<ref name="County history"/>

==經濟==
[[File:Safeway_store_sign_in_Lakeview,_Oregon..jpg|thumb]]
拉克夫由擁有幾所學校、一家醫院、一家鋸木廠、珍珠岩礦山和不少農業相關建築。拉克夫由亦擁有兩個鈾礦坑，而這兩個礦坑是於1955年至1960年代期間運作。<ref>{{cite web |url=http://yosemite.epa.gov/R10/CLEANUP.NSF/sites/WhiteKing |title=Fremont Nat. Forest Uranium Mines (USDA) |author=EPA |accessdate=May 3, 2013 |archive-date=2015-04-18 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150418102423/http://yosemite.epa.gov/R10/CLEANUP.NSF/sites/WhiteKing |dead-url=no }} <br/> {{cite web |url=http://www.clui.org/section/lakeview-disposal-cell |title=Lakeview Disposal Cell |author=Center for Land Use Interpretation |work=Perpetual Architecture: Uranium Disposal Cells of America |accessdate=May 3, 2013 |archive-date=2020-08-01 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200801211557/http://www.clui.org/section/lakeview-disposal-cell |dead-url=no }}</ref>附近的華納溪懲教設施於2005啟用。<ref name="prison">{{cite web|title=Issue Brief 2012: Warner Creek Corrections Facility|publisher=Oregon Department of Corrections|url=http://www.oregon.gov/DOC/OPS/PRISON/docs/pdf/ib_wccffacts.pdf|format=PDF|accessdate=July 6, 2013|deadurl=yes|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20140726133023/http://www.oregon.gov/DOC/OPS/PRISON/docs/pdf/ib_wccffacts.pdf|archivedate=2014年7月26日}}</ref>但監獄則因很多選民的反對而沒有興建。<ref>{{cite news|last=Esteve|first=Harry|title=Budget Squeeze Pressures Plan for New Prison|work=The Oregonian|location=Portland, Oregon|date=April 21, 2003|edition=Sunrise|page=B01}}</ref>距離本城的監獄為本城以北{{convert|4|mi|km|0}}的最低設防監獄。<ref name="prison"/>

拉克夫由亦於近年開始大力發展旅遊業，發展項目包括釣魚、賞鳥、露營、登山、滑翔、滑翔傘、攀岩、狩獵、野生動物觀賞和野花觀賞。<ref>{{Cite web |url=http://www.oregonsoutback.com/towns/index.html |title=Welcome to Lake County - Oregon's Outback<!-- Bot generated title --> |access-date=2013-07-15 |archive-date=2021-02-13 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210213220228/http://www.oregonsoutback.com/towns/index.html |dead-url=no }}</ref>本城以其懸掛式滑翔和滑翔傘活動聞名。本城更於1991年獲得「西方滑翔首都」之稱號。<ref>{{Cite web |url=http://www.cascadeparaglidingclub.org/pages/lakeview.php |title=Cascade Paragliding: About the club<!-- Bot generated title --> |accessdate=2013-07-15 |archive-date=2017-10-28 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20171028201734/http://www.cascadeparaglidingclub.org/pages/lakeview.php |dead-url=yes }}</ref>本城亦以熱間歇泉「獵人的溫泉」（Hunter's Hot Springs）聞名。該間歇泉在2009年6月以來已沒有再爆發。<ref name="Out of Steam">{{cite news|last=Preusch|first=Matthew|date=February 21, 2010|title=Lakeview's Iconic Geyser Seems to Be Running Out of Steam. But Why?|work=The Oregonian|url=http://www.oregonlive.com/environment/index.ssf/2010/02/lakeviews_iconic_geyser_seems.html|accessdate=2010-02-22|archive-date=2018-07-19|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20180719084029/https://www.oregonlive.com/environment/index.ssf/2010/02/lakeviews_iconic_geyser_seems.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>

